cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with point cloud data and shape analysis tasks such as classification and segmentation. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes a novel architecture for deep learning. The paper may also be relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with 3D shape analysis. Finally, it may be relevant to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category as it proposes a new pooling operation for PCNN.
